name: Inkbots #003
description:
A series of digital Rorschach inkblots generated from a 'random walk' algorithm which draws lines from the center of the canvas and randomly changes its length, direction, thickness, and color per segment, until it reaches a randomly-determined number of segments.

Glance at the Inkbot and answer two questions:
i) What do you see?
ii) Are you human?
